01:47:05,196 --> 01:47:07,031
- Hey, Derek.
- Hey.

1456
01:47:08,033 --> 01:47:09,241
Derek.

1457
01:47:09,409 --> 01:47:11,910
- We need to talk.
- What's going on?

1458
01:47:12,078 --> 01:47:15,956
