- How bad?

1460
01:47:18,543 --> 01:47:20,794
Well, it looks like they're gonna live.

1461
01:47:20,962 --> 01:47:24,048
- Then they got lucky.
- Somebody's gotta lose, though.

1462
01:47:27,260 --> 01:47:28,969
Aw, what?

1463
01:47:29,137 --> 01:47:32,264
