you'd talk to your old crew.

1464
01:47:32,432 --> 01:47:34,600
- Come on. No way.
- This is not a good thing.

1465
01:47:34,768 --> 01:47:36,935
If there's anybody they'll listen to,
it's you.

1466
01:47:37,103 --> 01:47:39,355
