a fucking bit of difference.

1479
01:48:17,644 --> 01:48:19,186
It might.

1480
01:48:20,605 --> 01:48:22,981
Do you know what you're asking me to do?
Do you really know?

1481
01:48:23,149 --> 01:48:26,235
Yes. I'm asking you to do
whatever is in your power to do.

1482
01:48:29,322 --> 01:48:30,656
Man.

1483
01:48:32,617 --> 01:48:34,118
Fuck.

1484
01:48:39,082 --> 01:48:40,666
