1486
01:48:44,963 --> 01:48:47,673
- I doubt it.
- Yeah, well..

1487
01:48:47,841 --> 01:48:51,218
we're all gonna have a laugh at that,
let me tell you.

1488
01:48:51,386 --> 01:48:54,638
I'm gonna take him to school.
I'll be back in half an hour.

1489
01:48:54,806 --> 01:48:56,181
Come on.

1490
01:48:56,349 --> 01:48:59,643
Hey, you. You got
something good for me this morning?

1491
01:48:59,811 --> 01:49:03,355
- I'll give it to you, Dr. Sweeney. All right?
- Yeah, okay.

1492
01:49:07,694 --> 01:49:09,194
What's going on?

1493
01:49:14,701 --> 01:49:16,160
Come on.

1494
01:49:32,051 --> 01:49:35,053
This is so bad for Seth, man.

1495
01:49:35,221 --> 01:49:38,390
- I wonder how bad they got fucked up.
- I don't know.

1496
01:49:38,558 --> 01:49:41,560
I'm glad they're not dead,
but other than that, I don't care.

1497
01:49:42,395 --> 01:49:43,687
Should we visit them?

1498
01:49:43,855 --> 01:49:45,981
Visit them? No. No, definitely not.

1499
01:49:46,149 --> 01:49:48,484
Definitely not. Just stay out of it.

