when I pulled out of there with Seth.

1502
01:49:54,824 --> 01:49:57,618
If you get home before me,
look around the street, all right?

1503
01:49:57,785 --> 01:49:59,745
Make sure there's nothing going on.

1504
01:50:01,164 --> 01:50:03,040
Oh, man. This is bad.

1505
01:50:05,460 --> 01:50:08,337
- They're after you, man.
- It'll cool off.

1506
01:50:08,505 --> 01:50:10,172
If I made it through Chino..

1507
01:50:10,340 --> 01:50:13,926
this should be a piece of cake, right?

1508
01:50:14,093 --> 01:50:17,262
- Are you gonna be okay?
- Yeah, yeah.

1509
01:50:18,681 --> 01:50:20,098
Okay.

1510
01:50:20,683 --> 01:50:22,142
What are you gonna do?

1511
01:50:22,310 --> 01:50:24,061
I don't know. I'll work it out. Hey.

1512
01:50:24,229 --> 01:50:26,355
Keep your head up.
Things are gonna be fine.

1513
01:50:26,523 --> 01:50:28,357
It's gonna be fine.

1514
01:50:28,525 --> 01:50:30,234
Go turn that paper in.

1515
01:50:32,445 --> 01:50:35,113
