1528
01:52:59,884 --> 01:53:03,929
Oh, no. No! No! No!

1529
01:53:04,263 --> 01:53:06,431
Oh, Jesus.

1530
01:53:09,060 --> 01:53:10,936
No.

1531
01:53:11,104 --> 01:53:15,273
Oh, no, no. No.

1532
01:53:29,831 --> 01:53:31,540
Oh, Jesus.

1533
